---
title: Sweet and Spicy Tofu Bibimbap with Fried Egg and Quick Pickles
description: Tofu is given new life in these Korean-inspired bibimbap bowls. It's cubed, oven-baked and smothered in a sweet, savoury and spicy sauce, then served alongside a medley of veggies and topped with a gooey fried egg. Get ready for an epic dinner adventure!
